<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Australia, China (Xizang, Yunnan*), Fiji, India (Andaman Is, Arunachal Pradesh*, Assam, West Bengal), Indonesia (Java, Maluku, Sumatra), Laos, East &amp; West Malaysia, Myanmar, New Guinea, Philippines, Solomon Islands, Sri Lanka, Thailand, Vietnam.</paragraph>
